==English==

===Etymology===
From English prefix '''[[ignorant|ig-]]''', as in'' ignorant'', + '''[[gnostic]]''', ''knowing''

===Noun===
'''ignostic''', plural '''ignostics''' 

# one who holds to [[ignosticism]] 
# one who expresses ignorance of any knowledge of a god or gods due to finding theism incoherent 

===Adjective===
'''ignostic'''

# of or relating to ignostics
# of or relating to ignosticism

